{"tid":1824192,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"原來牛肺飯唔影得，好怕今晚會有人聚集影響生意","createTime":"2020-01-14T09:14:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-14T10:20:58.000Z","uid":154702,"like":40,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"59d798bcd26a78cd8ecc3229ed9ccb60c49a10f4","tid":1824192,"uid":154702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T09:14:42.000Z","msg":"本身約咗朋友今晚果邊食飯<br />\n點知晏晝有年輕人被無理對待<br />\n好擔心今晚去食飯嘅行程受到影響<br />\n<br />\n希望唔會有太多人聚集<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n影響人哋做生意就唔係咁好<br />\n<br />\n我諗如果每次有便衣無理對待年輕人<br />\n之後都會有人聚集的話<br />\n警方會兩難<br />\n一心想保護藍店<br />\n另一方面太大反應又影響佢做生意<br />\n<br />\n話唔定藍店寧願息事寧人起碼有生意交租<br />\n都唔想有狗係附近搞搞震<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n噢<br />\n夠鐘出門口去食飯了"},{"pid":"6280caf569c0d5899aba2d3d68018c4f096b3e7d","tid":1824192,"uid":35456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T09:16:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"05f011f68cff5d0ffefd71e701dc6822f743697b","tid":1824192,"uid":83910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T09:17:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c18a7d89b59f9e7536cc7eaceb61b517dfd82e35","tid":1824192,"uid":9566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T09:18:35.000Z","msg":"去搞粉絲見面會了"},{"pid":"468af3a5375fe3a7e275caa027395e5c3517fbbd","tid":1824192,"uid":180902,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T09:19:22.000Z","msg":"肚餓 有冇人想一齊食飯？<br />\n提議下"},{"pid":"47f2eab556e74d3e0a8735bea916e9d44b118dea","tid":1824192,"uid":329698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T09:20:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4744a44134082f612c2fb89e6ea73ea2e8a8096","tid":1824192,"uid":154702,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T09:21:17.000Z","msg":"如果我係老細<br />\n我真係屌佢老味<br />\n而家已經生意唔好<br />\n人哋影一影相<br />\n其實本身都唔直接影響生意<br />\n都俾人影慣<br />\n<br />\n但係咁樣搞一搞擺上網<br />\n全部人放工過嚟搞鳩我<br />\n我成晚真係白交租<br />\n<br />\n如果隔離左右做唔到生意仲死<br />\n本身食肆都互相向食環投訴㗎啦<br />\n呢啲潛規則嚟<br />\n依家擺到明10間搞我一間<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f2e3be93fb69a64e2c422bc912767445912ecb3","tid":1824192,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T09:22:29.000Z","msg":"間藍店而家出晒名了"},{"pid":"5863286199bd4fde8de93860e10d71b26923fafa","tid":1824192,"uid":2156,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T09:23:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6N8XRBs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6N8XRBs.jpg&h=fec3b1dd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c50da318971ac12c1d79ec8bdfef4640688c3932","tid":1824192,"uid":8732,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T09:24:30.000Z","msg":"不如直頭落閘算啦<br />\n<br />\n新年3大任務：119大遊行，年廿八和手足團年，各區和你宵，幫手share 比親戚朋友一齊過黃色新年啦<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1822470\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1822470</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eHvn2J4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeHvn2J4.jpg&h=55a6086b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9660852014be7de45c9fdc67225797ad85a2db40","tid":1824192,"uid":136186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T09:24:46.000Z","msg":"一齊去影爆佢"},{"pid":"311c93575bc34e5560e0476c75553b7675a77536","tid":1824192,"uid":295124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T09:26:13.000Z","msg":"唔好去啊 真係唔好聚集 會做唔到生意"},{"pid":"9b35094bc33ac0d816aa070286098842f2cd8865","tid":1824192,"uid":43553,"like":0,"dislik